Quamachi2 is a python2-compatible Hamachi GUI for Linux.
It lies in the system tray.

Quamachi2 is an improved version of the latest python2-compatible
Quamachi available, it is more user-friendly than its predecessor
(Quamachi 0.4.5 by Xavion).
Icon theme has been redesigned.

Make sure sudo works for your user.
